edu.siu.cs.dagGen

Class DAGParse

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.siu.cs.dagGen.DAGParse

  • public class DAGParse
extends java.lang.Object
    DAGParse is a class that wraps the functionality and complexity of reading in a DAG file generated by this library. It reads in a file and returns the adjacency matrix representing a DAG.
    Author:
    crackerz
